# INPUT ELEMENTS

- PLC (Allen-Bradley MicroLogix / Siemens / Arduino with SCADA integration)
- IR Sensor – For bottle presence detection
- Solenoid Valve – For liquid dispensing control
- Relay Module – To switch solenoid valve or motor
- Power Supply – 5V / 12V / 24V DC as per component ratings
- SCADA Software – Wonderware InTouch 10
- HMI – Developed using InTouch WindowMaker
